===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The outlet at the end of a hose which is designed to [[atomize]], [[spray]], or [[mist]] the contents flowing through the hose. Typical use includes [[gaseous]] materials such as [[w:nitrous oxide|nitrous oxide]] in [[automotive]] applications, as well as [[fuel]]s for [[turbine]] engines.

